Title: Ek ladka aur ek ladki kabhi dist nahi ban sakte... Kyu?
Narrative:
Isn't it so weird that these days we normalise love more than friendship? So much so that if a boy and a girl are friends the movies try to motivate everyone that there's no such thing between a girl and a boy normalising not only love but also forcing love in friendship. 

This normalisation honestly not only pressurises love but also normslises heterosexual relationships. I feel it's high time people need to change this mindset and live the new normal ✌🏻
